quran[109]{c,v,t}:
  10,1,"Alif, laam, Raa, …óeen ko aayeeje deftere √Īe√Īaande ndeen."
  10,2,"Kere wonan yim…ďe …ďeen kaawasee, fii min wahyii- ma e gorko jeyaa…óo e ma…ď…ďe, won¬īde : ""jeertin yim…ďe …ďe? mbeltiniraa gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďe won¬īde no woodani …ďe nokku goongaajo ka Joomi ma…ď…ďe? heeefer…ďe …ďe mbi : ""oo ko mbileejo pee√Ī…óo""."
  10,3,"Pellet Joomi mon ko Alla on tak…óo kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin ndeer bal…óe jeegoo, refti o fotondiri ka dow Arsi, hombo toppitoo fiyakkuuji …óin. Alaa woo e tefoowo si wanaa …ďaawo duŇčayee makko. Ko on mo'on woni Joomi moo…óon, ndewee mbo. E on ciftorta?"
  10,4,"Ko ka makko woni ruttorde mon on denndaangal, ko fodoore Alla gooŇču…ónde! Ko kaŇčko woni fu…ó…óude tagoore nde, refti o ruttita nde fii yo o yo…ďa …ďeen gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďe ngolli golle mo∆ī∆īe e nun…óal. …ďeen heefer…ďe kan, hino woodani …ďe njaram immorde e fatay…óam, e lepte muusu…óe sabu ko …ďe laatinoo hi…ďe njedda."
  10,5,"Ko kaŇčko woni ba…ó…óo naange ngen jalbunge e lewru ndun nur…óundu, o e…ď…ďani ndu jippor…óe fii yo on anndu emmbere duu…ďi …óin e limoore ndeen Alla tagiraani …óiin si wanaa e goonga. hombo fensitana aayeeje …óen yim…ďe anndoo…ďe."
  10,6,"Hino e luutindirgol jemma e √Īalama ngol, e kon ko Alla tagi ka kammuuli e ka leydi, maandeeji wonan¬īde yim…ďe gooŇč…óu…ďe."
  10,7,"∆Āen …ďe njoortaaki hawrugol e amen, …ďe mbeltori nguurndam aduna …óam, …ďe dee∆īiri …óam, e …ďeen welsindii…ďe e aayeeje amen …óeen,"
  10,8,"∆Āeen, jaa∆īorde ma…ď…ďe nden ko Yiite ngen, sabu …óuum ko …ďe paggittonoo."
  10,9,"Pellet, …ďeen gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďe ngolli golle mo∆ī∆īe, joomi ma…ď…ďe feewnay…ďe e gooŇč…óinal ma…ď…ďe ngal. Caatli no ila ley ma…ď…ďe ka aljannaaji dokke."
  10,10,"Noddaandu ma…ď…ďe nder ton, ko ""Ya Alla senaade woodaniima"", salminaandu ma…ď…ďe ndu toon, ko : ""Salaam"", [kisal]. Ko woni wattannde noddaandu ma…ď…ďe, ko : ""jettoore ngoodanii Alla, Jey…óo Winndere ndeen""."
  10,11,"Sinno Alla yaccinanayno yim…ďe …ďen bone wano o yacciniranta …ďe mo∆ī∆īere, lajal ma…ď…ďe ngal timminanteno …ďe. min, ngacca …ďe …ďe tam∆īinaaki kawrugol e amen e bewre ma…ď…ďe nde he…ďe bumam-bumannoo."
  10,12,"Si lor memii ne…ó…óaŇčke o, o nodda min …ďaŇčŇče makko, maa ko joo…óii…óo, maa ko o darii…óo. tuma nde min ku√Īcini mo lor makko o, o fe∆ī∆īira wa si o noddaano min e lor mem…óo mo. Ko wano noon …ďurtinoo…ďe …ďeen cu…óiranaa ko ko …ďe ngollaynoo."
  10,13,"GooŇč…óii min kallkiino gire adinoo…ďe on nde …ďe too√Īnoo, nulaa…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďeen ngaddani …ďe …ďanngannduyeeji. …ďe wonaano gooŇč…óinoo…ďe. Ko wana nii min njo…ďirta yim…ďe bon…ďe …ďeen."
  10,14,"Refti min mba…ói on lomtotoo…ďe ka leydi …ďaawo ma…ď…ďe, ha min ndaara no ngollirton."
  10,15,"Si aayeeje amen …ďanngu…óe …óeen njanngaama e dow ma…ď…ďe, …ďeen …ďe tam∆īinaaki kawrugol e amen mbi'a: ""Addu Alqur'aanaare goo hara wanaa ndee …óoo"" maa ""wostonde"". maaku : haananaa kam nde mi wa…ótitira nde immorde e …ďaŇčŇče wonkii am. mi jokkataa si wanaa kon ko wahayinaa e am. min mi…óo huli si mi yeddii joomi am, lepte √Īalaande mawnde""."
  10,16,"Maaku : ""Sinno Alla muuyuno, mi janngataano nde e dow moo…óon, mi aanndintaande mon kadi. GooŇč…óii mi √Īii…ďiino e moo…óon nguurndamado may- re. e on haqqiltaa?""."
  10,17,"Alaa …ďur…óo too√Īude haa hewta on pekifindii…óo fenaande e hoore Alla, maa o yenni aayeeje makko …óeen. Si ko woni, o malnatah bon…ďe …ďen."
  10,18,"He…ďe ndeewa ga Alla …óuum ko lorrataa …ďe nafataa …ďe, he…ďe mbi'a : ""Ko …óii …óoo ngoni tefanooj amen …ói ka Alla"". Maaku : ""E on njweetoto Alla ko o anndaa ka kammuuli wanaa ka leydi?"" Senayee woodanii mo, O toowii gaay e ko …ďe sirkata."
  10,19,"Yim…ďe …ďe laatanooki si wanaa mofte goote. ∆Āe lurri. Sinno wanaa konngol adinoo ngol immorde ka Joomi maa, √Īaaweteno hakkunde ma…ď…ďe e …óuum ko …ďe lurraynoo."
  10,20,"He…ďe mbia : ""Ko ha…ónoo aaya njiippinee e makko immorde ka Joomi makko?"" Maaku : ""ngannde ko wirnii kon ko Alla woodanii.padee; min komi pat…óo wonndude e mo'on""."
  10,21,"Si minn mee…óinirii yim…ďe …ďe yurmeende …ďaawo lorra memnooka …ďe, jaka yoo he…ďe mari pewje e aayeeje amen …óeen. Maaku : ""Ko Alla …ďuri yaawude pewjugol"". Pellet, Nulaa…ďe amen …ďen he…ďe mbinnda kon ko pewjoton."
  10,22,"Ko kaŇčko woni doginoowo on ka njorndi e ka maayo, haa si on wonii ka laa…óe, …óe ndoknira …ďe henndu laa…ďndu, …ďe weltora ndu. Ara e majje henndu bippooru, molloo…óe (bempejje) …óen ara e ma…ď…ďe immorde e kala baŇčŇče, …ďe pellita won¬īde kam…ďe …ďe hu…ďindaama, …ďe toroo Alla ko …ďe la…ď…ďinana mo diina kan, […ďe mbi'a]: ""Si a da…óndii amen e …óum …óoo, pellet, men laatoday e yettoo…ďe [ma] …ďeen."
  10,23,"∆Āaawo nde o da…óndi …ďe, e jaka yoo kam…ďe he…ďe bewira ko leydi ko adaa e goonga. eehey mon yim…ďe, ngandee bewre mon nden yantay e woŇčkiiji mon. Ko dakamme nguurndam aduna. refti ko ka amen woni rutorde mon, min kaalano on ko laatino ho…óon ngolla."
  10,24,"Nganndee misal nguurndam aduna …óam, ko wano ndiyam …óam minn njippini immorde ka kammu, pu…ói leydi ndin jillondira e majjam …óum ko yim…ďe e neemoraa…ói √Īaamata. Haa si ndi leydi ndi ∆īettii cu…óaari mayri ndi cu…óike, yim…ďe mayri …ďen jikka won¬īde ko …ďe hattam…ďe (so√Īugol) e mayri, yami- roore amen ardira e mayri jemma maa √Īalorma, minn mba…óa (pu…ói) …óin so√Īaa…ói wa si tawii …ói mo∆ī- ∆īaano hanki mun. Ko wano nii min fensitirta aayeeje …óe wonan¬īde yim…ďe miijitotoo…ďe …ďen."
  10,25,"Alla no nodda on faade e galle kisal, hombo fewna on mo o muyyi faade e laawol pocciingol ngol."
  10,26,"Hino woodani …ďeen mo∆ī∆īim…ďe (golle) mo∆ī∆īere e …ďeydaari. Nduggu hippataa geece ma…ď…ďe …óen, wanaa kadi koyeera. Ko …ďen woni yim…ďe Aljanna …ďen, kam…ďe ko …ďe duumotoo…ďe ton."
  10,27,"∆Āeen faggitii…ďe boneeji …óin, njo…ďdi bone ko yeru makko. Koyeera hippay …ďe, Alanaa …ďe immorde ka Alla hay da…óndoowo, A sikkay jeece ma…ď…ďe …óen ko hippiraa ko ta∆īontinnde jemma ni…ď…ďut…óo. Ko …ďeen ngoni yim…ďe yiite, kam…ďe ko luttoo…ďe toon."
  10,28,"√Ďande min moo…ďindirta …ďe denndaangal, refti min mbi'ana …ďene sirkunoo…ďe : ""ngonee e nokku mon, onon e kafidii…ďe mon."" min senndindira hakkunde ma…ď…ďe, kafidii…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen mbi'a : ""wonaa minen ngono…óon e rewde""."
  10,29,"Alla yonii seedee hakkunde amen e mon. Si ko woni, min laatinoke welsindii…ďe ga e dewe mon …óen."
  10,30,"Ko …óon woŇčkii kala jarriborte ko ki ardinnoo. …ďe nduttee ka Alla gi…óo ma…ď…ďe on ka goonga; ko …ďe ngonnoo e fefindaande kon majjira …ďe."
  10,31,"Maaku : ""Ko hommbo arsikata on immorde ka kammu e ka leydi? Kaa ko hommbo jeyti nan…óe …óen e gii…óe …óen, ko hommbo kadi yaltinta ko wuuri e ndeer ko maayi, o yaltina ka maayi e nder ko wuuri, ko hommbo kadi yiilata fiyaaku on?"" …ďe mbi'ay : ""Ko Alla"". Maaku : ""e on kulatah?""."
  10,32,"Ko oon …óoon mo'on Alla, woni jey…óo on e goonga. Ko hol…óum woni …ďaawo goonga si wanaa majjere? Ko honno pirlitirte …óon?"
  10,33,"Ko wano nii konngol joomi maa ngol jojjiri e hoore yaltu…ďe …óoftaare …ďen :won¬īde pellet, …ďe ngooŇč…óintah."
  10,34,"Maaku : ""Hara no e kafidii…ďe mon …ďen oon mb no fu…ó…óa tagoore refi o ruttita nde […ďaawo maayde]?"" Maaku :""Ko Alla fu…ó…óata tagoore nde refti O ruttita nde Ko honno fefindara …óon [faade e meere]?"""
  10,35,"Maaku : ""Hara no e kafidii…ďe mon …ďeen on feewnoowo e goonga?"" Maaku: ""Alla no feewna e goonga. E ko on peewnoowo e goonga …ďuri haandude e jokkeede, kaa ko on mo feewanataa (hoore mon) si wanaa o feewna? Ko he…ďi on sifa no √Īaawirton?"
  10,36,"Ko …ďuri …óuu…óude e ma…ď…ďe jokkah si wanah sikke. Pellet sikke …óen nafataa e goonga kan hay e huunde. Pellet Alla ko ganndu…óo ko …ďe ngollata."
  10,37,"Sellatah ka ndee Alqur'aanaa fefindiree gaanin Alla, si ko woni, ko nde gooŇčginnde ko woni yeeso mayre, e fensitunde deftere, sikke alaa e mayre, ko nde immorde ka Jey…óo winndere nden."
  10,38,"Kaa …ďe mbiat : ""o fekindi nde?"" Maaku : ""ngaddee cortewol(simoore) yeru mayre, noddon kala mo kattan…óon ga Alla, si on laatike gooŇč…ďe""."
  10,39,"Ko woni, …ďe njeddii ko …ďe ku…ďindaaki ganndal mun, [ko …ďe fenniri nde], ko nde tawnoo firo mayre araani …ďe taho. Ko wano non adinoo…ďe …ďen fennirnoo. Ndaaru ko honno battane too√Īoo…ďe …ďen wa'unoo."
  10,40,"No e ma…ď…ďe gooŇč…óin…óo nde, no e ma…ď…ďe kadi mo gooŇč…óinaa nde. Ko Joomi maa …ďuri anndude bonnoo…ďe …ďeen."
  10,41,"Si …ďe njeddii ma, maaku : ""No woodani kam (njo…ďdi) golle am, no woodani on (njo…ďdi) golle mon. Onon ko on his…ďe ko mi gollata, min kadi ko mi kis…óo ko ngolloton""."
  10,42,"No e ma…ď…ďe …ďeen he…óotoo…ďe ma. E ko annannta faa…óu …ďe …ďeen, hay tawii …ďe haqqiltah?"
  10,43,"ino e ma…ď…ďe on ndaaroowo ma. e ko aan fewnata bum…óo oon, hay si wonii …ďe nji'atah?"
  10,44,"Pellet Alla too√Īirta yim…ďe …ďeen huunde, ko woni, ko yim…ďe …ďe too√Īata ko'e muen."
  10,45,"√Ďande o moo…ďoyta …ďe, wa'ata kona si …ďe √Īii…ďaano si wanaa sa'a gooto e √Īalawma, he…ďe nganndandira hakkunde ma…ď…ďe. GooŇč…óii …ďeen yeddu…ďe kawral Alla ngal sooyii, …ďe ngonaano feew…ďe."
  10,46,"Si min kollii ma yoga e ko ko min podani…ďe, maa …óuum min ∆īettitii ma, (fow e mun), ko faade ka amen woni ruttorde ma…ď…ďe. refti Alla ko ceedii…óo e ko …ďe ngollata ko."
  10,47,"Hino woodani mofte kala nulaa…óo. Si nulaa…óo ma…ď…ďe on arii, √Īaawiree hakkunde ma…ď…ďe nuun…óal, kam…ďe …ďe too√Īetaake."
  10,48,"He…ďe mbi'a: ""Ko honnde tuma woni ndee fodoore, si on laatike gooŇčgu…ďe?"""
  10,49,"Maaku : ""mi waawanaa hoore am lorra wanaa nafa si wanaa ko Alla muuyi. Hino woodani mofte kala lajal. Si lajal ma…ď…ďe ngal arii, …ďe nee…ďnirantaake saa'a …ďe ngardinantaake kadi""."
  10,50,"Maaku : ""kaalaneekam, si lepte makko …óe ngarii e mon jemma maa √Īalawma, ko hol…óum bon…ďe …ďe hawjiranta …óe?"""
  10,51,"E ko tuma …óe yani ngooŇč…óin ton …óe? e ko jooni noon, gooŇč…óii on laatinoke he√Īanii…ďe …óum?"
  10,52,"Refti too√Ī…ďe …ďen mbi'anee : ""mee…óee lepte luttugol. hara on njo…ďete si wanaa kon ngonno…óon e faggitaade?"""
  10,53,"He…ďe kabrino maa : ""…óuum ko goonga?"" maaku : ""Ko non, mi woo…óndirii joomi am, pellet ko …óe goonga. on ngonaani roŇčkinoo…ďe""."
  10,54,"Sinno tabitanno kala woŇčkii too√Īki jeyno ko woni leydi, ki sottorayno …óum. …ďe cuu…ói nimse …óeen …ďaawo nde …ďe nji'i lepte …óe. √Īaawiree hakkunde ma…ď…ďe nuun…óal, kam…ďe …ďe too√Īetaake."
  10,55,"Ngandee ko Alla woodani ko woni ka kammuuli e ka leydi. Ngandee pellet, fodoore Alla nde ko goonga. Kono ko …ďuri …óuu…óude e yim…ďe he …ďe nganndaa."
  10,56,"KaŇčko Hombo wuurna hombo wara; ko faade ka makko nduttote…óon."
  10,57,"Eehey mon yim…ďe, gooŇč…óii waaju arii e mon immorde e Joomi mon, e lekki fii (√Īabbuuji) ko woni e …ďer…óe, e peewal, e yurmeende wonannan¬īde gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďe."
  10,58,"Maaku : ""[Ko addan-mi on kon] ko …ďural Alla e yurmeende makko; yo …ďe mbeltor …óum …óon. Ko …óuum …ďuri mo∆ī∆īude ko …ďe moo…ďata""."
  10,59,"Maaku : ""kaalaneekam, …óuum ko Alla jippinani on e arsike, mba…ó…ó…óon e mun ko harmi e ko dagii? -maaku : ""Ko Alla duŇčanii on? kaa ko e Alla pekinto…óon (penaale)?"""
  10,60,"Ko hol…óuum woni sikke …ďeen fekindotoo…ďe fenaande e Alla, √Ďande Darngal? Pellet, Alla ko Joom …ďural e dow yim…ďe …ďen. Kono ko …ďuri …óuu…óude e ma…ď…ďe njettatah (dokkem …óe)."
  10,61,"A wonatah e fiyaaku, a janngataa e mayre e janngannde (alqur'aana), on ngollataa e gollal si wanaa minn ngoonat seedii…ďe e moo…óon tuma nde ngonoton e mun. Wirnotaako gaay e joomi maa yeru abbere jarra, wonaa ka leydi wonaa ka kam- mu; wonaa ko …ďuri …óum fam…óude, wonaa ko …ďuri mawnude si wonaa no e ndeer deftere …ďanngunde.(fee√Īnde).."
  10,62,"Nganndee yim…ďe Alla …ďe, kulol alanaa …ďe, …ďe ngonah sunoytoo…ďe."
  10,63,"∆Āeen gooŇč…óin…ďe, …ďe ngoni huloo…ďe [Alla]."
  10,64,"Hino woodani …ďe welo-welo ka nguurndam aduna e ka laakara. - Alaa bayloowo konngu…ói Alla …óin -. Ko …óum woni malal mawngal."
  10,65,"Wota konngol ma…ď…ďe sunine. Pellet, teddungal ngal denndaangal ko Alla woodani. Ko kaŇčko woni Nanoowo, ganndu…óo."
  10,66,"Nganndee ko Alla heeranii …ďeen won…ďe ka kammuuli e …ďeen won…ďe ka leydi. eko …ďeen noddoo…ďe gah Alla njokkaani e kafidii…ďe? …ďe jokkaani si wonaa sikke, …ďe ngoonaani si wonaa fenoo…ďe."
  10,67,"Ko KaŇčko woni ba…óan…óo on jemma on fii yo on ndee∆ī e maako, e √Īalawma on jii'r…óo. Pellet, wonii e …óum maandeeji wonann¬īde yim…ďe nanoo…ďe."
  10,68,"∆Āe mbi'i : ""Alla jogitike …ďi…ó…óo"". Senaade woodanii mo! Ko KaŇčko woni galo jon di…óii…óo on. Hino woodani mo …óuum ko woni ka kammuuli e …óuum ko woni ka leydi; alanah on cemmbe e …óuum. E on wowlay Alla ko on nganndaa?"
  10,69,"Maaku: ""Pellet, …ďeen fekindotoo…ďe fenaande e Alla …ďe maletaake""."
  10,70,"Ko dakamme ka aduna, refti ko ka amen woni ruttorde ma…ď…ďe nde refti min mee…óina …ďe lepte cattu…óe …óen sabu ko …ďe njeddiraynoo ko."
  10,71,"Janngan …ďe kabaaru Nuuhu, tuma nde o maakan-no yim…ďe makko …ďen: ""Ko onon yo yim…ďe, si tawii √Īii…ďugol am (hakkunde mon) mawnii e mon, e baa- jorgol lam Aayeeje Alla …óe, ko e Alla woni ko mi fawii. Haray pellitee fiyaaku mon on, e kafidii…ďe mon …ďeen. refti wota fiyaaku mon on wonan on ko mugii. refti pewjanon kam (ko paala…óon), wota on nee…ďtinanam."
  10,72,"Si on nduŇčtiima, mi lamndaaki on njo…ďdi, njo…ďdi am ndi wonaani si wonaa ka Alla. mi yamiraama nde mi laatotoo e jebbilii…ďe …ďeen""."
  10,73,"∆Āe njeddi mo. minn da…óndi mo kaŇčko e wondii…ďe makko …ďeen ka laana. min mba…ói …ďe lomtotoo…ďe (e leydi). min njooli …ďeen yeddunoo…ďe Aayeeje amen …óen. Ndaar ko honno battane jertinaa…ďe (salii) …ďeen wa…ói."
  10,74,"Refti minn immini …ďaawo makko nulaa…ďe haa e yim…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen. ∆Āe ngaddani …ďe …ďanngannduyeeji. ∆Āe ngonaano gooŇč…óinoo…ďe sabu ko njeddiri …óuum ko ko adii. Ko wano nii min notirta e …ďer…óe …ďeen jaggitu…ďe.(yawtu…ďe keeri)."
  10,75,"Refti minn immini …ďaawo ma…ď…ďe Muusaa e Haaruuna haa e Fir'awna e mbatu mun, won`dude e Aayeeje amen …óen. ∆Āe mawnikini, …ďe ngoni yim…ďe bon…ďe."
  10,76,"Nde goonga kan ari e ma…ď…ďe immorde e amen, …ďe mb'i : ""…óum …óoo ko mbilewu pee√Īngu""."
  10,77,"Muusaa maaki: ""E on mbi'anay goonga kan tuma ka ari e mon : E nee ko mbilewu nii? Hara le wilju…ďe …ďen maletaake""."
  10,78,"∆Āe mbi'i : ""E a ar e amen fii yo a yiltu amen e ko min tawri ko baabiraa…ďe amen …ďe, mawngu ngun laatano on onon …ói…óo ka leydi? Minen min ngonaani gooŇč…óinoo…ďe on""."
  10,79,"Fir'awna wi'i : ""ngaddanee kam kala bileejo aganndu…óo""."
  10,80,"Nde wilee…ďe …ďeen ngarnoo, Muusaa maakani …ďe : ""Bugee(mberne) ko bugoto…óon kon""."
  10,81,"Tuma nde …ďe buginoo, Muusaa maaki : ""Kon ko ngaddu…óon ko ko mbilewu, pellet, Alla bonnay …óum. Pellet, Alla mo∆ī∆īintah golle bonnoo…ďe …ďeen""."
  10,82,"Alla no tabintinira Goonga kan Konngu…ói makko …óin, hay si bon…ďe …ďen nga√Īii."
  10,83,"GooŇč…óinaano Muusaa si wanaa ge√Īngol( …ďesngu)e yim…ďe makko …ďen, sabu kulol Fir'awna e mbatu ma…ď…ďe ngun, nde …ďe fitinta …ďe. Pellet, Fir'awna ko townintinoo…óo ka leydi, pellet, ko e fantim…ďe …ďen o jeyaa."
  10,84,"Muusaa maaki: ""Eehey mon yim…ďe am, si on laatike goos…óin…ďe Alla, haray ko e Makko pawoto…óon si on laatike jebbilii…ďe""."
  10,85,"∆Āe mb'i : ""Ko e Alla min koolori. Joomi amen, wota wa…ó amen fitina wonan¬īde too√Īoo…ďe …ďeen."
  10,86,"Da…óndiraa men yurmeende maa nden e yim…ďe heefer…ďe …ďeen""."
  10,87,"Min wahayini faade e Muusaa e neene-gooto makko on, won¬īde: ""njippinee yim…ďe mon …ďen Misra e cuu…ói, mba…óon cuu…ói mon …óin fewtu…ói (qibla), √Īii…ďnon julde nden. mbeltinaa gooŇč…óiin…ďe …ďen""."
  10,88,"Muusaa maaki: ""Joomi amen, A okkii Fir'awna e mbatu mum ngu cu…óaari e jaw…óeele ka nguurndam aduna, Joomi amen, fii yo …ďe majjin gaay e laawol Maa ngol. Joomi amen, mehu(momtu) jaw…óeele ma…ď…ďe …óen, uddaa …ďer…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen, hara …ďe ngooŇč…óintaa haa …ďe nji'a lepte muus…óe …óeen""."
  10,89,"O daali: ""GooŇč…óii toraare mon nden jaabinaama. √Ďii…ďee (e diina), wota on njokku laawol …ďeen …ďe nganndaa""."
  10,90,"Min lummbini …ďi…ó…ďe Israa'iila …ďen maayo ngon. Fir'awna konu mun ngun njokkitiri …ďe bewre e jaggitere. Haa nde joolagol ngol hewtitii mo, o wi'i: ""mi gooŇč…óinii won¬īde dewetee…óo Alla si wonaa on mo …ďi…ó…ďe Israa'iila …ďen ngooŇč…óini. min ko mi jeyaa…óo e jebbilii…ďe …ďeen"".(juul…ďe …ďe)."
  10,91,"E ko jooni non? GooŇč…óii a yeddiino ko ado, njeyaya-…óaa e bonnoo…ďe …ďeen."
  10,92,"Hannde minn da…ódnirte …ďanndu maa ndun, fii yo a wonan …ďeen aroo…ďe …ďaawo maa…óa tasakuyee. Pellet, ko …óuu…ói e yim…ďe …ďen gaay e aayeeje amen …óen ko welsindii…ďe."
  10,93,"GooŇč…óii minn weernii …ďi…ó…ďe Israa'iila …ďen weerde teddunde, min arsike …ďe immorde e laa…ďu…ói. ∆Āe lurraali haa nde ganndal ngal ari e ma…ď…ďe. Pellet, Joomi maa √Īaawoya hakkunde ma…ď…ďe √Ďande Darngal, e kon ko …ďe luutondiraynoo e muu…óum."
  10,94,"Si a wonii e sikkitaare e …óuum ko min njippinii e maa…óa, lanndii …ďen …ďe no jannga deftere nden ado maa…óa. GooŇč…óii goonga kan arii maa immorde ka Joomi maa, wata a jeye e …ďen sikkitii…ďe."
  10,95,"Wata a jeye e …ďeen yeddu…ďe aayeeje Alla …óen, laato-daa e sooyu…ďe …ďeen."
  10,96,"Pellet, …ďeen …ďen konngol Joomi maa ngol jojji e mun …ďeen …ďe ngooŇč…óintah."
  10,97,"hay si arii e ma…ď…ďe kala aaya, haa …ďe nji'a lepte muusu…óe …óeen."
  10,98,"Mee…óaani laataade e ho…óo gooŇč…óingo, gooŇč…óinal ma…ď…ďe nafi …ďe si wonaa yim…ďe yuunusa …ďen. Nde …ďe ngooŇč…óinnoo, minn kuncanno …ďe lepte koyeera …óen ka nguurndam aduna, min dakmiti …ďe haa e saanga."
  10,99,"Sinno Joomi maa muuyuno, won…ďe ka leydi …ďen fof ngooŇč…óinayno. E an a doolay yim…ďe haa …ďe ngoona gooŇč…óin…ďe?"
  10,100,"Laatanaaki wooŇčkii nde ki gooŇč…óinta si wonaa e duŇčayee Alla. Homo wa…óa so…ďe [lepte] …óen e hoore …ďeen …ďe kaqqiltaa."
  10,101,"Maaku: ""Ndaaree ko hol…óum woni ka kammuuli e ka leydi"". aayeeje …óe e jertinooje …óe nafatah yim…ďe …ďe ngoo…óintaa …ďen."
  10,102,"Hara he…ďe habbii si wonaa yeru √Īan…óe …ďen fe∆ī∆īunoo…ďe ado ma…ď…ďe? Maaku: ""cabbitee, min mi…óo wonndi e mo'on jeyaa…óo e sabbitii…ďe …ďen""."
  10,103,"Reft mnn nda…ónda nulaa…ďe amen …ďen e …ďeen gooŇč-…óin…ďe. Ko woni non jojjiri e amen da…óndugol gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďe."
  10,104,"Maaku: ""eeheymon yim…ďe, si on wonii e sikkitaare e diina am, (miin) mi rewataa …óiin …ói dewoton gaa nin Alla; ko mi rewata, ko Alla oon baroowo on. mi yamiraama nde mi laatotoo e gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďen""."
  10,105,"E won¬īde : ""√Ďii…ďin yeeso maa ngon diina kan ko o oo√Īii…óo, wata a wonu jeyaa…óo e sirkoo…ďe …ďeen""."
  10,106,"Wota a noddu gah Alla, …óuum ko nafatah ma lorrataa ma. Si a wa…óii (…óuum), an dey haray a jeyaama ontuma e too√Īoo…ďe …ďeen""."
  10,107,"Si Alla meminirii ma lorra, alaa k√Īuncoowo mo si wonaa KaŇčko. Si o faandike e maa…óa mo∆ī∆īere, alaa duttoowo …ďural makko ngal. Homo memina nde on mo o muuyi e jeyaa…ďe makko …ďeen. Ko KaŇčko woni jaafotoo…óo, jurmotoo…óo on."
  10,108,"Maaku : ""Eehey mon yim…ďe, gooŇč…óii goonga ka arii mon immorde ka Joomi mon. Kala peewu…óo, e haray ko hoore-makko o feewani; kala kaadi majju- …óo, haray ko e makko defii. min wonaani pawaa…óo e hoore-mon."
  10,109,"Jokku ko wona ko e wahayineede ko e maa…óa, mu√Ī√Īo-…óaa haa Alla √Īaawa. Ko KaŇčko woni …ďur…óo mo∆ī∆īude e √Īaawoo…ďe."
